Unnamed Package

  • Class
    Description
    Account
    Abstract class representing a bank account.
    BankManager
    Represents a Bank Manager with special privileges and responsibilities.
    BankManagerMenu
    Implements the Menu interface for bank manager operations.
    BankOperations
    Manages all banking operations and coordinates between users and the system.
    BankStatement
    Generates bank statements for customers including personal information, account details, and transaction history.
    Checkings
    Represents a checking account with the ability to transfer funds.
    Credit
    Represents a credit account where the balance is negative, with a set credit limit.
    CSVHandler
    Handles all CSV file operations for the banking system.
    Customer
    Represents a bank customer with all their personal information and accounts.
    CustomerMenu
    Implements the Menu interface for customer operations.
    Menu
    Menu interface defines different types of menus in the banking system.
    NewUsers
    Handles the creation of new bank users and their accounts.
    Person
    Abstract class for representing people in the banking system.
    RunBank
    Main class for the banking application.
    Savings
    Represents a savings account with the ability to transfer funds to another account.
    TransactionHistory
    Handles the generation of transaction history files for customers.
    TransactionLog
    Handles logging of all banking transactions.
    TransactionProcessor
    Handles the processing of transaction files for the banking system.
